commitResults.messageTitle: Update logic and test cases for Find Command
commitResults.messageBody:
Find command allows duplicate prefixes to be input as the
parameters. This causes the duplicated prefix to override
the keywords in the previous prefixes.

Allow only one instance for each prefix so that previous
search terms are not overriden.
Clean up cosmetics in UG and UI

commitResults.messageTitle: Update fields to remove extra whitespace
commitResults.messageBody:
Parser currently does not remove additional whitespace
between words. This makes the fields extremely hard to
read when user adds extra whitespaces, whether
intentionally or accidentally.

Remove additional whitespaces between words, leaving
only one space to improve readability.

Products with multiple words cannot be added
successfully. This hinders users' ability to
add certain products.

Allow products with multiple words to allow a
greater range of products that can be added.
